dct_alternative_sm: Historical United States county boundary files
dct_description_sm: "Contains ArcView shapefile format county boundary files for the contiguous United States from each decade from 1790 through 1990 (also 1999). Files include county and state names as well as FIPS identification numbers and county area estimates. Territories enumerated by the U.S. Census are also included."
Carville Earle, Samuel Otterstrom, John Heppen.
System requirements: Windows 95 or higher, or Windows NT 4.0 or higher ; ArcView, ArcInfo or compatible software.
dct_creator_sm: Louisiana State University (Baton Rouge, La.), Department of Geography and Anthropology
